Interface Summary
DataMapListener An interface for a listener interested in DataMap changes.
DataNodeListener For managing the changes in the DataNode
DbAttributeListener For managing the changes in the DbAttribute.
DbEntityListener Defines a listener for DbEntity modification events.
DbRelationshipListener For managing the changes in the DbRelationship.
DomainListener For managing the changes in the Domain
ObjAttributeListener Listener for ObjAttribute events.
ObjEntityListener For managing the changes in the ObjEntity
ObjRelationshipListener Defines a listener for ObjRelationship modification events.
ProcedureListener Listener for Procedure events.
ProcedureParameterListener Listener for ProcedureParameterEvents.
QueryListener Listener for QueryEvents.
 

Class Summary
AttributeEvent Represents events resulted from Attribute changes in CayenneModeler.
DataMapEvent An events describing a DataMap change.
DataNodeEvent Represents events resulted from DataNode changes in CayenneModeler.
DomainEvent Represents events resulted from DataDomain changes in CayenneModeler.
EntityEvent Represents events resulted from Entity changes in CayenneModeler.
MapEvent Superclass of CayenneModeler events.
ProcedureEvent An event generated when a Procedure object is added to a DataMap, removed from a DataMap, or changed within a DataMap.
ProcedureParameterEvent  
QueryEvent An event generated when a Query object is added to a DataMap, removed from a DataMap, or changed within a DataMap.
RelationshipEvent Represents events resulted from Relationship changes in CayenneModeler.
